page.title: 20TYPICAL DAYS
page.content: Caretaker:woke up turned off alarm\put kettle on\ made tea\made packed lunches \got cereal ready ate it\woke son up\peeled potatoes\cleaned yard\feed rabbits\came over to school\ put toilet rolls,towels out\walked round school to check it\let pupils in\had a cup of tea\talked to Mrs G\ tidied woodwork room\mended broom\fed dogs\lunch\took wife to hospital\had dinner\came back to school\took cupboard to pieces\ stacked chairs\ mopped coffee up\locked doors\ closed windows\ went home\ took dog for a walk\watched T.V.\went to bed.
